NUMBER 1409
NAME Shadow's Realm
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The place you have entered has no signs of light or dark. Images and shapes
constantly shift and move. There is no pattern, all is chaotic. Just when
you think you know what something is, it is not. Reality and its laws
seem to have no hold here. You wonder what strange type of being would want
to call this place home. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 206
ITEM 0 84
