  SPELL 511 100
  SPELL 326 100
  SPELL 133 100
  SPELL 102 100
  SPELL 130 100
ENDIF

IFSAY Shadows_aid_me
  SPELL 510 100
  SPELL 515 100 
  SPELL 521 100
  SPELL 520 100
  SPELL 209 100
ENDIF
; <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<Yarin Medallion>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
INUMBER 1843
NAME 135
ARMOR
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE SOFTMETAL
CONTAINER ON
INTERIOR 2
WORN_DON
*DESCRIPTION_START
The medallion is formed from beautiful platinum, with the glimmering gemstone
set into its center. The Rune of Yarin is apparent on its surface.
*DESCRIPTION_END  

IFPREVERB GAZE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks deep into the medallion of Yarin.
  SHOWROOM ITEMVAL1
ENDIF

IFPREVERB RUB -1
  IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 1
    IFVAR ORG = 25
      IFVAR RNUM = 442
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You concentrate upon the medallion of Yarin and call on the knowledge of your patron to welcome a new member.
        ECHO OTHERS %N concentrates upon %h medallion, a gift of Yarin. %H medallion appears to elongate and suddenly splits into two, the second one dropping to the ground.
        ECHO PLAYER You feel Yarin's blessing and knowledge enter you, and your medallion splits into two halves and each becomes a whole.  The new medallion drops to the ground.
        NEWITEM 9 1843 ADJ1=111 ADJ2=1343
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  IFVAR RNUM = 344
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You gaze intently at your medallion, allowing it to draw your mind and eventually your body elsewhere....
    ECHO OTHERS %N stands rigid - deep in concentration.  Ever so slowly %s fades from sight.
    MOVE 441
    AFFECT 441
    ECHO OTHERS %N slowly fades into sight beside you.
    AFFECT 344
  ENDIF
    IFVAR RNUM = 441
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You gaze intently at your medallion, allowing it to draw your mind and eventually your body elsewhere....
      ECHO OTHERS %N stands rigid - deep in concentration.  Ever so slowly %s fades from sight.
      MOVE 344
      AFFECT 344
      ECHO OTHERS %N slowly fades into sight beside you.
      AFFECT 441
    ENDIF
  ENDIF

IFPREVERB PULL -1
  IFITEM -1 WORN
    IFVAR RNUM = 344
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You gaze intently at your medallion, with a firm grasp on your comrades you allow your mind to drift within carrying them along.
      ECHO OTHERS %N stands rigid - deep in concentration.  Ever so slowly %p fades from view.
      MOVEGROUP 441
      AFFECT 441
      ECHO OTHERS %P slowly fades into sight beside you.
      AFFECT 344
    ENDIF
      IFVAR RNUM = 441
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You gaze intently at your medallion, with a firm grasp on your comrades you allow your mind to drift within carrying them along.
        ECHO OTHERS %N stands rigid - deep in concentration.  Ever so slowly %p fades from view.
        MOVEGROUP 344
        AFFECT 344
        ECHO OTHERS %P slowly fades into sight beside you.
        AFFECT 441
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF

IFPREVERB WEAR -1
  ECHO PLAYER A binding force seems to take hold of you, and the medallion glimmers slightly.
  ECHO OTHERS %N's medallion glimmers slightly.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB REMOVE -1
  IFVAR RNUM ! 442
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You grasp the medallion and attempt to remove it.  You find that you are unable to do so.
    ECHO OTHERS %N appears to be struggling with the medallion on %h chest.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You grasp the medallion in the presence of your patron and remove it.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
 
IFPREVERB GET -1
  IFVAR ORG ! 25
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER The medallion of Yarin scampers away from your hand like a thing alive.
    ECHO OTHERS %N reaches for the medallion on the ground causing it to skip away from %h hand.
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB TAP -1
  IFITEM -1 WORN
    IFVAR REGION = 0
      CLEARVERB
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 25 25
      DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY DUMMY1 You call upon Yarin to guide you. You feel weakened as the medallion drains you. 
      EQUAL ITEMVAL1 RNUM
      ECHO OTHERS %N grasps Yarins's medallion and is suddenly bathed in a brilliant emerald light.
      ECHO OTHERS The emerald light begins to fade away and.....
      ECHO OTHERS %N is no more.
      AFFECT 441
      ECHO OTHERS %N appears in an emerald flash.
      AFFECT ITEMVAL1
      MOVE 441
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB TOUCH -1
  IFITEM -1 WORN
    IFVAR RNUM = 441
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO OTHERS %N grasps Yarins's medallion and is suddenly bathed in a brilliant emerald light.
      ECHO PLAYER You close your eyes and can see the last room you called upon Yarin's hand to guide you from.
      ECHO OTHERS The emerald light begins to fade away and.....
      ECHO OTHERS %N is no more.
      AFFECT ITEMVAL1
      ECHO OTHERS %N appears in an emerald flash.
      AFFECT 441
      MOVE ITEMVAL1
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
