NUMBER 442
NAME Pool of Reflection
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 441
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The entire chamber is bathed is a shimmering glow which appears to radiate from
a large pool in the center.  A feeling of quiet calm, mirrored by the unmoving
surface of the water fills your soul, inviting you to lose your mind's eye
within its depths.  This is an ancient place....a place of power and history 
of which few remaining mortals know the existance of....it is here that the
faithful of Yarin come to induct newcomers into their Circle.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 324 ADJ1=287
EXTEND 0 of still water
ITEM 1 744 VAL2=441
EXTEND 1 which seems to waver slightly

IFTOUCH 0
  CLEARVERB
  IFCARRY 1843 -1
    ECHO PLAYER You lay your hand against the cooling fluid of the pool and are warmed by its power.  Even this action does not cause any noticable motion along its surface.
    ECHO OTHERS %N places %h hand flat against the surface of the pool.  Interestingly, no waves of motion mar the surface at all.
  ELSE
    DAMAGEPLR COLD 25 The water is amazingly cold!  It seems to be sucking knowledge and power from your very heart...not physical power, but that derived from experiences and learning!
    ECHO OTHERS %N shrieks as %s pulls %h hand away from the pool's still surface!
  ENDIF
ENDIF        

IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The pool is very large and holds some kind of deep, internal glow.  The most remarkable feature of the entire thing is the fact that nothing causes even the 
  ECHO PLAYER slightest ripple in its surface.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GAZE 0
  IFCARRY 1843 -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You look deep into the waters of the pool and are surrounded by thoughts of places lost but through time and history, races unborn and long past, and events yet to be...
    ECHO OTHERS %N appears to be lost in deep concentration.
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER Deep within the pool, you see an image. A library, stacks of books like those in the library of Fayd, attended by three aged highlanders..
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER You see a phantasmal form pass among them, unnoticed save for a slight chill. Slowly, slowly, the female spirit is searching through the stacks.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER The pool turns dark for a moment, then seems to shift, showing possible events rather than current ones...
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER You see Gildren kneeling, tears streaming down his face as he yells into the sky. The image moves down and you see a body with a ragged claw mark across its chest...the image moves up and you see the face of the dead body....
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER ..It is Calia.....
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT 
    ECHO PLAYER ....once again the image moves to that of a figure standing behind the two, wrapped in shadows and a dark robe the only thing about the figure you can make out is one gloved hand extended, its thin bloody fingers grasped around a necklace.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT 
    ECHO PLAYER The images swirl and cease to have further meaning.
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Fleeting images seem to tickle your mind just beyond reach.
    ECHO OTHERS %N appears a bit perplexed as %s gazes at the waters of the pool.
  ENDIF
ENDIF 
