bookcase which lines the western wall.  Standing nearly twenty feet high and
running a length of three times that you wonder where anyone would ever find
enough books and tomes to fill the whole thing.  If it were not for the loans
granted a starting Yarin Circle by the other Circle's, you are sure that the
shelves would be nearly bare.
