NUMBER 1408
NAME Sage's Hall
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A bookcase covers each of the walls in this large room. They are filled with
scrolls and books of various age and size. A counter stretches the entire
back wall. Behind it stands an friendly looking elderly woman. Like the
mages also in this room she wears the medallion of Yarin. On the counter is
a small sign. You notice the vending machine has moved to the next room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1112
ITEM 1 60 VAL2=443
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
Printed on the sign is the following:

	Night Vision		10  Gold
	Body Restoration Two	50  Gold
	Mystic Armor		50  Gold
	Cold Shield		60  Gold
	Heat Shield		70  Gold
       	Camouflage		70  Gold
	Spectral Shield		90  Gold
	Cure Disease		120 Gold
	Globe			150 Gold
   	Strength Three		160 Gold
	Repel Webs		180 Gold
   	Mass Protection		230 Gold
 	Globe Two		300 Gold
        Regeneration            300 Gold

Please note: To have spell cast please simply state the spell name.
             If you lack the proper funds no spell will be cast.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFENTRY
  SPELL 250
  IFCARRY 1843 -1
    IFITEM -1 WORN
      ECHO ALL All the mages bow deeply to %N.
    ENDIF
    ELSE
      ECHO ALL The elderly women says, "Hello there, I hope you enjoy our services."
    ENDIF
  ENDIF


IFSAY night_vision
  IFVAR WEALTH > 999
    ECHO PLAYER One of the mages chants a spell and casts it upon you.
    ECHO OTHERS One of the mages chants a spell and casts it at %N.
    SUB WEALTH 1000
    SPELL 520 40
    ADD PVAL13 10
  ENDIF
ENDIF

